{"tid":566390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡派錢，收入越高派得越少","createTime":"2018-02-20T01:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T06:32:50.000Z","uid":38671,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2f4feaa139027cd514ca21212347fc8ea0d9ac3c","tid":566390,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T01:53:49.000Z","msg":"新加坡政府公布2018/19年度財政預算案，預計去年錄得96億坡元財政盈餘。新加坡財長王瑞傑公布，所有滿21歲國民今年可按收入獲得100至300坡元「紅包」（約600至1,800元），約有270萬人受惠。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">新加坡政府建議，年收入達2.8萬坡元（約16.7萬港元）或以下國民可獲派300坡元；年收入10萬坡元（約59.6萬港元）可獲派200坡元；年收入超過10萬坡元或持多個一個物業可獲派100坡元。</span><br />\n<br />\n為應付未來社會於基建及教育等方面的增加開支，預算案亦提出於2021年至2025年間上調消費稅 (GST）兩個百分點，由目前7%增至9%，具體推出時間則視乎當地經濟及開支情況而定。<br />\n<br />\n此外，新加坡亦計畫課徵每噸5元新幣碳稅（carbon tax）。自2020年起亦會向進口服務課徵e-tax，包括網上影片及音樂串流平台等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180219/57850950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180219%2F57850950&d=zPblo4S34Y2ngGBY31oUIi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=4c04c148\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180219%2F57850950&h=4778c3ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180219/57850950</a>"},{"pid":"f3d2d3d06a4710a184549787719186cd3b2d4c1e","tid":566390,"uid":51920,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T01:56:17.000Z","msg":"好彩冇去新加波<br />\n唔係分分鐘要收番我錢"},{"pid":"3b3272ec9db819f9bde020f5ae781f4f8505fbd3","tid":566390,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T02:00:00.000Z","msg":"咁少 真係食餐飯"},{"pid":"9008c38f298bea0dd1321b0a1df6262619e9f6a8","tid":566390,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T02:00:28.000Z","msg":"上網都要收稅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d615619364087b